reviewText: It's suppose to depict the intricate lives of 3 presidents but the transition from old president to new president was POORLY done; couldn't understand what was happening so had to repeat scenes.

I love all Asian movies and dramas but this is one , is one of the best I have ever seen. So much great acting and movie really pulls at your heart strings . It was worth buying. If you have never tried the Asian drama and movie wave this would be a great start.
